  "description": "A dramatically lit image showcases two segments of a peeled orange resting on a highly reflective, dark surface. The orange segments appear translucent, with visible juice cells and a bright, warm glow emanating from within. The lighting is directional, creating strong highlights and shadows, and emphasizing the texture of the fruit and the surface below. The dark background intensifies the contrast, drawing the viewer's eye to the orange segments. The reflection of the orange segments on the surface is nearly a mirror image, contributing to the overall symmetry and visual interest. The angle suggests a low viewpoint, enhancing the prominence of the fruit.",
